Package io.artframework.parser.flow

Interface FlowLineParserProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Provider, Scoped
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultFlowLineParserProvider
    public interface FlowLineParserProvider
extends Provider
    The flow line parser provider allows the registration of custom parsers that are iterated when parsing a list of flow lines.

    Register an implemented FlowLineParser with this provider and they are automatically used when a List<String> is parsed by the FlowParser.
